////////////////////////////////////////////////
// Proof by Cases (or-) Tool
//
// A simple example of the proof by Cases tool.
// Compare to BIH Cases.lurch

Declare or
Rules:
{ 
  cases> :{ :W or V  :{:W U}  :{:V U}  U }  
  :{ :W   W or V   V or W } 
}
// this should pass   
{ :P or Q
  { :P  Q or P}
  { :Q  Q or P}
  Q or P by cases
} ✔︎
// but this should fail, even with the cases rule labeled above
{ :A or B
  { :A  B or A}
  { :B  B or A}
  B or A
} ✗